  "instructions": [
    "Wrap each trout fillet in a banana leaf and place on a steamer basket.",
    "Steam the trout over boiling water for 8 minutes, or until cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, mix the fried shallots, nam prik sauce, fish sauce, lime juice, and chopped cilantro in a small bowl.",
    "Once the trout is cooked, place it on a serving platter and spoon the nam prik sauce mixture over the top.",
    "Top with sliced Thai chilies, mint leaves, and crushed peanuts.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with a sprinkle of coconut milk and a drizzle of rice vinegar.",
    "Garnish with additional mint leaves and banana leaves, if desired."
  ],
